    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/4e274f732ad5c59821d0fbfb5893ffdf.avif?t=1771648293\" width=473 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/718fb77fd386fa5f36b842907d2b0f5b.poster.avif?t=1771648293\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/718fb77fd386fa5f36b842907d2b0f5b.webm?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/718fb77fd386fa5f36b842907d2b0f5b.mp4?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>白晝下的集體恐懼</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >恐懼不在黑暗中潛伏，它在白日裡游走：儀式中、面具下、宿友的笑容裡。這裡的恐怖是群體的壓迫，是窒息的從眾。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>服從被監控，反抗必懲罰</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你以模範信徒身份開始：紀錄清白，完美笑容，遵循日常儀式。然而<strong>操行系統</strong>會審視你每個念頭、猶豫與拒絕。你的分數將決定你能否憶起過去，扭轉結局，甚至決定你是否真正自由。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d465ef94b93bda9e340000e05cb9e445.poster.avif?t=1771648293\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d465ef94b93bda9e340000e05cb9e445.webm?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d465ef94b93bda9e340000e05cb9e445.mp4?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>白天裡，偽裝成好信徒</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融入你的宿友，參與儀式，交換耳語，維持那張僵硬的面具。每一個舉動都被審視，每一句話語都可能成為證據。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>黑夜裡揭穿真相</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潛入禁區，駭入系統，挖掘被掩埋的歷史。但切記小心，因為<strong>「大人」無所不在</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/ce540285bc503ff73f28e0780dd0827e.poster.avif?t=1771648293\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/ce540285bc503ff73f28e0780dd0827e.webm?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/ce540285bc503ff73f28e0780dd0827e.mp4?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遺物的記憶</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集可以穿梭時空的遺物，將現在與過去連結，它們是唯一的鑰匙——能帶你離開，或將你徹底囚禁。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>手繪的亞洲邪教美學</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索超過 60 幅手繪場景與過場動畫，其靈感源自超現實主義與虛構的香港都市。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>電子樂的迷幻儀式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在金曲獎音樂製作人打造的電子聲景中，在欣快與恐懼之間反覆遊走，將你拉入這個邪教的懷抱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d2ae0f0fa3422f72b7053fe9c5db9436.poster.avif?t=1771648293\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d2ae0f0fa3422f72b7053fe9c5db9436.webm?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2098190/extras/d2ae0f0fa3422f72b7053fe9c5db9436.mp4?t=1771648293\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
